151
00:19:30,310 --> 00:19:32,640
Hay bất kỳ đầu mối nào?

152
00:19:38,920 --> 00:19:40,880
Soda.

153
00:19:42,690 --> 00:19:44,250
Mm.

154
00:19:44,790 --> 00:19:46,620
Rất hữu ích

155
00:19:47,990 --> 00:19:49,690
